reviewText: I must admit first off that I am a very big fan of almost anything made for British TV.  With that said the 'Yes  Minister' series if well written with outstanding actors.  The humor is low key with spurts of good belly laughs.  I am sorry they made so few Minister and Prime Minister shows.

reviewText: Not many places you can get good old BBC comedies. Amazon Prime is fantastic for all kinds of entertainment needs. The quality is great for such an archived show and the show as usual is entertaining.  If you love poking fun at the bureaucracy you will love this show.  If you are like me and love a great value Amazon Prime is something to look into purchasing.
